node.text:
My creativity has been put to the test this #circuitbreaker 🤯 My brain is exhausted coming up with ways to keep this little fella occupied. Thankfully @hasbrosingapore sent over a set of toys which helped to keep him entertained (and out of trouble!!) ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Ethan walks his toy kitty everyday 🐱 and after watching me cook, he pretends to bake cookies & make pancakes with @playdoh slime 🍪🥞 — I’m secretly hoping he’ll become a masterchef junior & take over our kitchen! Then I no need to cook lo, hooray!!! 😂
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Check out @hasbrosingapore official store on @shopee_sg! The toys are also available on @toysrus shop online, Amazon and Lazada
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
#hasbrosingapore #playtogether #bringhomethefun #circuitbreakersg #stayhome #sgunited
So cute! It's amazing how kids are so drawn to slimes 🔥🔥🔥
Wow!!! Reminds me of HDL noodles!!!
He looks like having a really great time
Wa second pic like a pro 😆
